<h3>Overview</h3>

Field layout and style can be defined using the following properties:

<h4>Field Style Properties</h4>
<ul>
  <li>field.captionstyle</li>
  <li>field.captionclass</li>  
  <li>field.controlstyle</li>
  <li>field.controlclass</li>
  <li>field.blockstyle (Only applicable if field.block=true)</li>
  <li>field.blockclass (Only applicable if field.block=true)</li>
  <li>field.cellstyle (Grid-only)</li>
  <li>field.cellclass (Grid-only)</li>
  <li>field.nl</li>
  <li>field.eol</li>
  <li>field.block</li>
  <li>field.nowrap</li>
</ul>

See the <a href="/tutorials/model_styling#grid_properties">Model Styling</a> tutorial for examples and more information.
